N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 180-3.31 - OCFS Policies and Procedures

State Regulations
OCFS may develop policies and procedures related to the
provisions of this subpart, any of which shall have the same force and effect
as the section of subpart 180-3 it is defining or explaining. Notes

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
